Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.00,0:00:04.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens, I'm still your partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.99,0:00:07.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today, one thing that's stolen is a life,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.37,0:00:09.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is that guy really responsible?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.44,0:00:10.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Recognizing that single truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.90,0:00:12.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a child with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.43,0:00:14.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.69,0:02:00.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri Kogoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.40,0:02:00.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.57,0:02:05.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why have you invited that famous detective here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.87,0:02:06.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:08.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm being targeted, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.37,0:02:11.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Targeted? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.08,0:02:16.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, it's because of what the art\Nworld has been anticipating for so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.92,0:02:20.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guren, Konjiki, Junbaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:21.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And now, Seiran.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.80,0:02:29.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who plans to soar to it through the darkness to take it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.14,0:02:34.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A notorious burglar known as "The Magician Under the Moonlight."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.85,0:02:36.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They call him Kaitou Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.52,0:02:38.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What'd you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.19,0:02:39.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I received a notice earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.19,0:02:46.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Tomorrow at 20:00, I'll come to collect my beloved\NSeiran from the cover of a full moon's glow."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.99,0:02:49.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Oh no, we have to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.24,0:02:52.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, I've called the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.16,0:02:57.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With him being an elusive magician with the ability to transform,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.50,0:02:59.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not so sure they're qualified.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.00,0:03:04.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No, that's not what I'm worried about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:06.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What if this ordeal leads them to... And the painting...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.76,0:03:08.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one will find out...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.09,0:03:11.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.76,0:03:15.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takeyori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, you mean you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:19.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was out of ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.44,0:03:20.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Takeyori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.12,0:03:23.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whatever you're planning, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.61,0:03:25.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What gives you the right to tell me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.24,0:03:30.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The way this has come together makes it your fault, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.53,0:03:35.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you must do it... I may have an idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.67,0:03:40.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.59,0:03:42.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just messing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.17,0:03:45.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a world famous artist, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.72,0:03:48.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could I do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.18,0:03:50.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, the notice was a joke as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.55,0:03:53.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I actually did get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.31,0:03:55.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.60,0:04:00.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whenever that famous detective Mouri\Nfaces him, Kaitou Kid never wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.69,0:04:04.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Especially since he began bringing that active little boy with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.86,0:04:07.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'll be able to protect this treasure, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.53,0:04:11.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That boy named Edogawa Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.83,0:04:16.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaitou Kid & the Four Masterpieces, Part One!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:23.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well now, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.96,0:04:27.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is your third bout with Kid. Will you beat him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.05,0:04:31.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't know until after it's over, but I don't think I'll lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.59,0:04:34.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, this isn't just the third time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.68,0:04:38.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you've faced him more than what's been in the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.14,0:04:41.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, what's the trick to beating Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.56,0:04:43.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I don't always beat him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:48.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, it's all due to the daily training\Nsessions taught by me, Mouri Kogoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.11,0:04:49.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, the famous detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.95,0:04:51.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a lucky kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.66,0:04:54.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, Detective, will you win?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.24,0:04:57.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean, against the world's greatest burglar?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.79,0:04:59.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.16,0:05:03.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, despite the chances involved...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.50,0:05:04.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'll suffer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:08.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chances and suffering, great, great...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.05,0:05:10.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why the hell're you here with your terrible puns!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.80,0:05:12.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-Inspector Nakamori...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.68,0:05:14.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is where Kaitou Kid said he'd show.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.22,0:05:18.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you grab that old fox Megure\Nand hunt down some murderers?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.64,0:05:20.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid you're mistaken, Inspector Nakamori.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.73,0:05:26.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was asked to come to this villa by Oikawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},\Nthe one who received the notice from Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:30.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, are the police fully prepared?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:33.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why has Kid switched from precious\Nstones to paintings all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.91,0:05:36.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One rumor claims that the notice itself was a hoax!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.04,0:05:38.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No comment!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.91,0:05:42.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How many times have I told you all not to get near the scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:48.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Oikawa's newest work is supposed\Nto be unveiled live on TV tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:50.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.38,0:05:51.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.34,0:05:55.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard the painting itself is done, but he's\Njust waiting until the revealing to sign it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:58.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that's if Kid doesn't steal it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.14,0:06:02.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this? You make it seem like he'll get it no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:03.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.31,0:06:10.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Regardless, don't enter the house until the warning time\Nof 8:00 PM has passed and we've secured the painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.15,0:06:11.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:15.99,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I've been expecting you, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.96,0:06:18.22,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Oikawa Takeyori (59)\NArtist
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.32,0:06:18.23,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm Oikawa Takeyori.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.51,0:06:19.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:24.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I had to bring my daughter along, I hope you don't mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.17,0:06:28.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, if you want, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and I can wait in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.42,0:06:33.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no. It's fine. I trust Detective Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.01,0:06:34.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's great to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.13,0:06:39.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, I've heard this little boy is that thief's counterpoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.22,0:06:44.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, let me show you where Seiran is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:45.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:46.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takeyori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.23,0:06:48.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I need to speak with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.02,0:06:52.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, can it wait a moment, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:55.77,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,That's your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:07:00.68,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kanbara Haruhito (82)\NTakeyori's Father-in-law
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:07:00.48,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's my wife's father and my teacher, Kanbara Haruhito.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.04,0:07:03.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You may recognize his name if I pronounce it as "Seijin" instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:06.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, the famous scenery painter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.62,0:07:11.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, he hasn't held a brush\Nin ten years due to his hand injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.51,0:07:17.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome to my workshop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.26,0:07:21.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is such a great atelier!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.06,0:07:26.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As you'd expect in Okutama, the only\Nscenery out here are mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.56,0:07:30.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Five riot officers just under the window...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.61,0:07:33.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I doubt he'll come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:39.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He could use his hang glider, but the\Nwindows seem like they're locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:42.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All this over this painting, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.33,0:07:43.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this is Seiran.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:45.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, let's take a peek...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:47.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't do that, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.79,0:07:52.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't like people seeing my work before its done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:55.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But isn't your signature the final touch?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.55,0:07:58.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, there are some small touch-ups I want to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:08:00.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.09,0:08:04.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All of these plaster models make this look like a school's art room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:07.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I teach art classes here once a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.06,0:08:11.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that a security camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:15.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I had it installed immediately after I received the notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:19.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can check the videos if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.49,0:08:21.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.58,0:08:29.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like both entrances have two guards each.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.71,0:08:32.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All four of them have pinch marks on their cheeks, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.79,0:08:35.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess that means Inspector Nakamori\Nhas already checked them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:39.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, we've only got thirty minutes until\Nthe announced time of 8:00 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.97,0:08:42.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone, be at your best and protect this painting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.80,0:08:45.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, this is the feed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.51,0:08:50.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean, the picture is very clear, but why's there only one camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.14,0:08:54.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When he told me he already had surveillance\Nequipment, I didn't expect a single camera either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.94,0:08:57.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I wasn't clear about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.90,0:09:01.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, why aren't there any guards in the atelier?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.03,0:09:03.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't allow anyone in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.12,0:09:06.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's possible one of them could peek at\Nmy painting like Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} almost did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.95,0:09:09.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My men aren't like that at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.75,0:09:12.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I guess having one is better than none.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.71,0:09:13.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.42,0:09:17.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but could you turn the camera off?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.92,0:09:21.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I need about ten minutes to do my final check.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.09,0:09:25.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's only thirty minutes until the announced time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.68,0:09:27.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll borrow this transceiver until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.77,0:09:29.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll contact you when I'm finished checking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.98,0:09:36.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:38.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're free to enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.44,0:09:39.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.28,0:09:40.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takeyori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.82,0:09:41.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.11,0:09:43.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:46.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm about to do my final check.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.37,0:09:49.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I have something to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.04,0:09:52.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.29,0:09:55.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you wait just a few minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.34,0:10:00.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Too long, just too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:03.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hell's he doing? It's been well over ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.51,0:10:05.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm finished, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.72,0:10:06.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can turn the camera back on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.51,0:10:08.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.60,0:10:12.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How is it? Is it working?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.10,0:10:15.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Now hurry and leave the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.66,0:10:16.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.86,0:10:21.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can talk now, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.11,0:10:26.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I wanna get a look at this painting even Kid wants to steal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:29.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's part of a four piece set.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.62,0:10:30.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A four piece set?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.12,0:10:33.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The first, Guren, was a flower,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:35.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the second, Konjiki, was of the moon,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:37.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the third, Junbaku, was a bird,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.25,0:10:41.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the fourth that Kid's after Seiran, should be of the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.92,0:10:44.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it! The four beauties of nature!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.47,0:10:48.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, he's trying to convey the four\Nbeauties through the four paintings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.01,0:10:53.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, I can see he used a flower, the moon,\Nand the wind, but why is Junbaku a bird?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.02,0:10:55.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a crone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:59.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The pointing is of on exotic, pure white\Ncrane in the middle of a snowfield.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.61,0:11:06.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, his last two works both fetched\Nhigh prices, so I'd say this one...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.74,0:11:08.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A blackout!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.28,0:11:09.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The lights are out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.58,0:11:10.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the circuit breaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.16,0:11:14.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys go check it out and get it back in order!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.87,0:11:15.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.87,0:11:16.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.96,0:11:19.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's still ten minutes left before the announced time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.13,0:11:22.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father! Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.25,0:11:22.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.96,0:11:23.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.80,0:11:24.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:27.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The old man was inside when the blackout occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.26,0:11:30.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why'd you let him go in?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.05,0:11:32.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He went in just as I was going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.81,0:11:36.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he didn't trust the police or some detective\Nto protect the painting and that he'd do it himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.35,0:11:43.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was on my way to get you, and the lights suddenly went out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.61,0:11:45.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's the key?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.11,0:11:48.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was hurrying to get in and dropped it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:49.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.87,0:11:50.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's break it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.49,0:11:53.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,1,2, 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.50,0:11:55.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.21,0:11:57.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.75,0:12:01.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You all below the window, have you seen anything!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.42,0:12:06.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We saw something fall from the window, which\Nlooks like some cups and some paint brushes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.26,0:12:08.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, the painting's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.59,0:12:14.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, it disappeared as if it were an illusion...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.97,0:12:15.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:18.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.02,0:12:21.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tainted with blood the color of a crimson lotus flower...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.31,0:12:23.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The old man's life faded away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.19,0:12:25.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.17,0:12:32.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaitou Kid killed someone!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.38,0:12:36.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I heard he's never hurt anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.51,0:12:37.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.64,0:12:41.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since Kid killed someone, the report's going to run awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.18,0:12:44.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it may even go well into tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.52,0:12:45.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you, over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.10,0:12:49.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're not doing anything, get us\Nsome drinks from the station car!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.23,0:12:52.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.03,0:12:52.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.99,0:12:56.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.83,0:13:02.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.33,0:13:06.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We heard that someone was murdered, is Kid responsible?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.92,0:13:09.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was it really the police's fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.17,0:13:11.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No comment, no comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.80,0:13:15.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's true that Oikawa's newest\Nartwork, Seiran, was stolen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.09,0:13:19.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You all are assuming Kid would never kill, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.97,0:13:20.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said no comment!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.35,0:13:24.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you comment on the investigation so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.31,0:13:26.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, let us through already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.27,0:13:30.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The weapons used were a knife and a stun gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.69,0:13:33.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a wound from the stun gun on the victim's neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.61,0:13:36.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanbara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} probably caught the culprit stealing the painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.99,0:13:42.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Figuring he'd been caught, the culprit used the\Nstun gun and then the knife to finish him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.37,0:13:44.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Any fingerprints?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.96,0:13:49.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,None on the stun gun, but Oikawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s\Nwas found on the handle of the knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.42,0:13:51.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, could he have...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.75,0:14:01.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, with it being that dark, he wouldn't be able\Nto find him immediately without a light source.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.89,0:14:09.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would say it's more likely he heard Kanbara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s yelping\Nand then felt around on the ground until he found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.77,0:14:12.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's probably when he touched the knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.82,0:14:18.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, when we broke the door down, we\Nheard the culprit exiting via the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.03,0:14:21.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the culprit was in the room before the blackout?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.83,0:14:27.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he was probably hiding in the ceiling and\Ncame out by the air conditioner after the blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.42,0:14:30.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why'd the blackout occur?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.63,0:14:36.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Several high-voltage devices were programmed with timers\Nto activate at the same time, causing the breaker to trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.26,0:14:40.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we'd been more cautious, we would have found them earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.76,0:14:44.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, Oikawo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} only just\Ngot the notice yesterday morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.56,0:14:48.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We weren't contacted with the information until last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.10,0:14:52.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That would mean he sent the notice only after\Nhe was done with the preparations, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.77,0:14:55.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then? Did anyone see the criminal escape out the window?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.19,0:15:00.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, we were prepared for him to come through\Nthat window, so we didn't spotlight it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.20,0:15:05.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That would've told everyone where the pointing was.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.79,0:15:12.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All we recovered were these two brush stands and some\Nbrushes that fell when he went out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.54,0:15:16.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, Megure, I'll leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.55,0:15:20.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can use the security camera video to identify the suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.38,0:15:23.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, isn't the criminal Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.05,0:15:24.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you the one who deals with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.76,0:15:26.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This guy isn't Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.97,0:15:29.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only thing he'd never steal is a life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.81,0:15:35.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure, the video from the atelier's\Nsecurity camera is ready to be played back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.86,0:15:37.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is an hour before the crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:40.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is right after the painting was checked...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.36,0:15:44.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this is the first image from after the power was restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:48.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know why there's a segment missing before and after the blackout,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.54,0:15:51.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but why is there a cut before and after he checked the painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.96,0:15:54.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They turned the camera off at my request.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.21,0:16:00.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If anyone sees my paintings before they're\Ncomplete, I can no longer appreciate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:03.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been my policy for the longest time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.51,0:16:08.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to Inspector Nakamori, Konbara-son went\Ninto the room after you finished your check, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.02,0:16:09.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.23,0:16:14.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he couldn't trust a detective\Nor the police to protect the painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.11,0:16:21.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father-in-law was being stubborn and refused\Nto leave, so I went to get Inspector Nakamori.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.24,0:16:27.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I left, locking the door just to be safe,\Nand then the blackout happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.95,0:16:33.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After I called out to him and he didn't reply,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.04,0:16:36.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I tried to get in but dropped my keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.67,0:16:41.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. That's why Inspector Nakamori broke\Nthe door down after he made it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.92,0:16:43.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But isn't it weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.47,0:16:48.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After you finished checking the painting,\Nyou were talking into the transceiver.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.22,0:16:55.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The video doesn't have sound, but you were telling\NInspector Nakamori that your check was done, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.19,0:16:57.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.77,0:17:00.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since Kanbara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} came in just after that,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.32,0:17:03.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,why didn't you use the transceiver to call for the inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.24,0:17:06.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because my father-in-law took the transceiver from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.28,0:17:08.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he wouldn't let anyone stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.70,0:17:14.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did hear that the transceiver was\Nfound on Kanbara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.96,0:17:17.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But can't we think of it this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.33,0:17:22.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the blackout, Kanbara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} decided\Nto protect the painting by hiding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.47,0:17:26.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There must be cupboards in the atelier\Nthat're used to store canvases.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.93,0:17:28.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.43,0:17:32.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be sure that if Kid did get\Ninside, he'd have nowhere to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.22,0:17:37.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, before checking the painting, I\Nlocked all of the canvas cupboards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.48,0:17:38.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the keys?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.61,0:17:41.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're with the atelier keys I lost during the blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.57,0:17:46.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think they were found in the hallway earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:51.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, we should assume someone\Nsnuck into the atelier in the dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.24,0:17:53.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.45,0:18:00.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before the blackout, the police officers guarding the doors\Nwould have checked to make sure they were locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.59,0:18:02.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Kid wouldn't really need a key...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.00,0:18:10.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I overheard Inspector Nakamori tell his men that\Nif there was a blackout, to grab the knobs and not let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.01,0:18:16.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means, someone was hiding in the ceiling and\Nappeared in the atelier during the blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.52,0:18:23.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After appearing, he killed Kanbara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who was inside the\Nroom, stole the painting, and escaped out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.44,0:18:28.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But is that something Kid would really do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.82,0:18:30.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't really say yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:34.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would seem he's never killed before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.33,0:18:36.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he may have finally given in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.75,0:18:39.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You sound anti-Kid to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.21,0:18:45.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course! Kaitou Kid is the archnemesis of the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.05,0:18:48.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have a reason to side with Kid, Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.09,0:18:50.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what if I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.97,0:18:54.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you know that the notice was real?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.72,0:18:57.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the picture Kid always draws on his notices.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.89,0:19:02.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He always draws a new one for each notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.15,0:19:06.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If someone were to copy one of them from a newspaper or from TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.65,0:19:08.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they would be caught instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.78,0:19:18.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But according to Inspector Nakamori, they checked and\Nare sure it's really him since the lines are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.25,0:19:22.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you know, someone that's good at\Ndrawing could be pretending to be Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.38,0:19:25.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like a mangaka, an illustrator, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.88,0:19:27.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe a painter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.80,0:19:30.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.26,0:19:31.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did say "maybe."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.01,0:19:35.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't draw anything silly like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.85,0:19:40.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking as a professional artist, I would say it's authentic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.39,0:19:42.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think so, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.94,0:19:44.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet it's Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.23,0:19:45.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a bad guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.36,0:19:49.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's use your wits to capture the bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.68,0:19:52.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, a phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.82,0:19:55.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.74,0:19:57.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have two phones?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.16,0:19:57.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.33,0:20:01.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, one's for work and the other's for private use.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.42,0:20:04.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of them seems to have blood on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.92,0:20:10.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After rushing to my bleeding father-in-law's aid, I called\Nsome relatives to inform them of the bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.55,0:20:12.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It probably happened then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.72,0:20:14.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.93,0:20:18.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you call me back later?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.39,0:20:21.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. May I go change?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.44,0:20:24.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm uncomfortable with all this blood on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.02,0:20:27.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let us search you first, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.36,0:20:32.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Nakamori already saw to that, but if you must.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.13,0:20:56.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've come to steal the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.10,0:20:58.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaitou... Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.44,0:21:11.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey man,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.36,0:21:14.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,any idea what's in this bag? It seems heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.90,0:21:16.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't touch it, don't touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.31,0:21:18.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll get fired for touching things without permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:19.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.91,0:21:22.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just noticed something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.50,0:21:23.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.58,0:21:27.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think there's something in your back pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.46,0:21:29.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.59,0:21:31.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.67,0:21:32.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.26,0:21:34.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a card!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.97,0:21:36.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaitou Kid!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.13,0:21:38.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a great find, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.68,0:21:42.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must have put this in your pocket before all of this happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.60,0:21:45.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep! I'll give it to the inspector right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.06,0:21:47.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you Kid did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.58,0:21:51.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or at least that's what you wanted to hear, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.28,0:21:53.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.94,0:21:57.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He figured a child would be excited\Nabout anything that involved Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.86,0:21:59.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he invited us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.41,0:22:05.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If this guy had prepared this card, he\Nwould have just left it at the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.54,0:22:08.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This means it's geniuine and he only just found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.25,0:22:13.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Nakamori would've never\Nmissed it if he had it on him back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.26,0:22:20.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means that card was definitely put on him after that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.01,0:22:26.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to rip your mask off once more, Kaitou Kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.94,0:22:31.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here tonight, under this full moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.56,0:24:04.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We cannot say this yet, but everything points to this option.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.38,0:24:10.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess there's no doubt that Kid's the murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.58,0:24:15.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A thought came to me that could serve as a clue.\NWill you let me demonstrate?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.67,0:24:16.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.02,0:24:20.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.69,0:24:25.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.05,0:24:28.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaitou Kid & the Four Masterpieces, Part Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.98,0:24:32.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.79,0:24:34.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Things you can't see, but still exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.55,0:24:37.06,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Did Kid really do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.08,0:24:38.09,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,He is a thief, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.13,0:24:39.08,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It is Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.09,0:24:39.56,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Well done!
